HEADWORD: Stick-seed
<hw>Stick"-seed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A plant (<spn>Echinospermum Lappula</spn>) of the Borage family,
with small blue flowers and prickly nutlets.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

